*Vidimo* se uskoro! (We'll see each other soon!)
Oni *vidimo* da je to istina. (They see that it's true.)
Ne *vidimo* se često. (We don't see each other often.)
Šta *vidimo*? (What do we see?)
Oni *vidim*o da je to istinito. (They saw that it was true.)
Da li *vidimo* šta se dešava? (Do we see what is happening?)